Daniel Eric Gold https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Eric_Gold 0 Daniel Eric Gold (born September 19, 1975 in Los Angeles, California) is an American actor. He attended Lee Strasberg's Theater Institute as a teenager, and went on to graduate from Penn State in 1996, with a degree in Theater Arts.
